# Build artifact: tool files are copied here from spec/tools/ before wheel
# build so that `uv_build` (which only packages content under the module root)
# includes them in the wheel.  The canonical copies live at spec/tools/.
#
# Populated by: python spec/scripts/populate_tools.py  (or `uv run` wrapper)
# Consumed by:  hotam_spec.cli._path_setup (adds this dir to sys.path when
#               the real spec/tools/ is absent, i.e. wheel-installed mode).
*
!.gitignore
